aces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />完全唔覆。唔知做咩膠。之後覺得佢由始至終玩嘢嘅成份高啲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f254bcabbe458f6b93ece680e5d9551a870de11d","tid":1982721,"uid":99299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"58877469b0600e24a467e87e2d52549d089c1df8","tid":1982721,"uid":230488,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e8c68b57e20906e66b5a06a5c8b857d4a121457e","tid":1982721,"uid":99299,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e5eab996ef90f79e16cd9a6538c46fa3187ea774","tid":1982721,"uid":230488,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:06:16.000Z","msg":"我就完全冇一思掛住﹐<br />\n之前係好嬲啲事﹐好討厭佢﹐依家完全唔感覺(好能已經睇清晒)..不過就剩返啲啲嘔心嘅感覺。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:14:00.000Z","msg":"前度喺一度傷痕 即使時間可以令佢癒合，但內心知道佢存在過<br />\n好難唔痛 ching係點做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋好嬲嘅係之前發生咩事?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:10:45.000Z","msg":"好多小事累積起來。<br />\n<br />\n妙嘅係 一開始一齊時 第六感就覺得 佢好似有很多事隱瞞。雖然表面係對我幾好﹐但硬係覺得我好似同個 &rdquo;殼&rdquo; 交緊往。只能夠傾表面開心嘅嘢。一去到要傾深入啲就逃避。（分咗知咩事.) <br />\n<br />\n其實到最未如果佢肯坦誠傾一傾 我都會放下﹐唔會咁討厭佢﹐應該可以做返朋友。但佢搵返我時候當我係老友? 好似冇嘢發生﹐同佢好friend咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我一提返佢就冷處理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />完全唔覆。唔知做咩膠。之後覺得佢由始至終玩嘢嘅成份高啲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:24:25.000Z","msg":"第六感通常都好準<img src=\"/assets/f